comprising Funcinpec, Sam Rainsy Party, Son Sann Party and Khmer
Neutral Party, will send a letter next week to U.N. Secretary
General Kofi Annan to reaffirm their support for the U.N. proposed
conditions for Cambodian elections.
</P>
<P>
