</P>
<P>
-- The Southeast Anatolian Project, which is of great
significance to the economic development of the backward Turkish
southeastern areas, is progressing smoothly, experts said Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Radikal (Radical)
</P>
<P>
-- Turkey will open a 500-million-U.S. Dollar tender late this
year to international and domestic defense companies for the
upgrading of Turkish army's aged M-60 tanks, unnamed military
sources said Thursday. 
