that of chemical products for information use increased by
18.7 percent.
</P>
<P>
An official from the bureau attributed the increase to the
industry's efforts to expand foreign trade.
</P>
<P>
Facing oversupply on domestic markets, firms producing caustic
soda and soda ash explored overseas markets, emerging as a factor
for the export increase, the official said. 
