<HEADLINE> China Sets Up Bureau of Nonferrous Metals Industry </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 24 (Xinhua) -- Sources of the State Council
announced here today that the State Bureau of Nonferrous Metals
Industry has been set up to replace the China National Nonferrous
Metals Industry Corporation (CNNMIC).
</P>
<P>
