<HEADLINE> Accredited Checking Officers Preparing to Do Their Job </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 24 (Xinhua) -- A group of 100 people will get a
two-month training course starting next week to give them
accreditation as checking officers for various big state-owned
enterprises, the Personnel Ministry said today.
</P>
<P>
"We are now preparing to send them to their job positions as
early as possible," said Song Defu, the Personnel Minister.
</P>
<P>
