for their consideration.
</P>
<P>
During the meeting, he briefed the commission on steps being
taken by the security forces to deal with the situation.
</P>
<P>
He said he was convinced that the police were winning the war
against crime, but it was a difficult situation and one could not
expect miracles overnight.
</P>
<P>
The commission also discussed ways of bringing "healing" to
the broken communities in the province. 
