<HEADLINE> Larsen Fails in Four-time European Champion Bid </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SOFIA, April 24 (Xinhua) -- Poul-Erik Hoyer-Larsen failed to
become the first four-time European badminton champion after
losing his semifinal to fellow Dane Kenneth Jonassen here on
Friday.
</P>
<P>
