<HEADLINE> Results of Monte Carlo Tennis (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, April 24 (Xinhua) -- Following are the quarter final
results of the 2.2 million U.S. dollars Monte Carlo Open men's
tennis tournament on Friday (prefix number denotes seeding):
</P>
<P>
14-Carlos Moya, Spain, bt 6-Alex Corretja, Spain, 6-3, 6-2
</P>
<P>
7-Richard Krajicek, Netherlands, bt 2-Petr Korda, Czech
Republic, 4-6, 7-6 (7/1), 6-1
</P>
